{"word":"G611 - ἀποκρίνομαι - apokrínomai - ap-ok-ree'-nom-ahee - Answer","slug":"G611","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποκρίνομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>apokrínomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ap-ok-ree'-nom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Answer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03BA;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - apokrinomai</b> - <i>ap-ok-ree'-nom-ahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G575\">G575</a> and <b>&#x03BA;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;</b> <b>krino</b>; to <i>conclude for oneself</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>respond</i>; by Hebraism (compare [<a href=\"#/H6030\">H6030</a>]) to <i>begin to speak</i> (where an address is expected): - answer."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1252\">G1252</a>, <a href=\"#/G1253\">G1253</a>, <a href=\"#/G1469\">G1469</a>, <a href=\"#/G178\">G178</a>, <a href=\"#/G2631\">G2631</a>, <a href=\"#/G2632\">G2632</a>, <a href=\"#/G2633\">G2633</a>, <a href=\"#/G2917\">G2917</a>, <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a>, <a href=\"#/G2920\">G2920</a>, <a href=\"#/G2922\">G2922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2923\">G2923</a>, <a href=\"#/G2924\">G2924</a>, <a href=\"#/G350\">G350</a>, <a href=\"#/G351\">G351</a>, <a href=\"#/G470\">G470</a>, <a href=\"#/G610\">G610</a>, <a href=\"#/G612\">G612</a>, <a href=\"#/G843\">G843</a>, <a href=\"#/G87\">G87</a>"}]}